member.remarks:
Deduplication level the percentage of fingerprint matches for deduplication. Valid values are -
None
Similar
HighlySimilar
VirtuallyIdentical
Default is 'Similar'.

member.name: F:Factiva.Services.Track.V1_0.TrackFolder.showDup
member.remarks: This specifies whether or not to list the ANs of the hits that were removed during deduplication. Default is False.

member.name: F:Factiva.Services.Track.V1_0.TrackFolder.deliveryContentType
member.remarks: deliveryContentType is set to eradicate flooding user emails ( when not online folders) with too many web hits, with the introduction of new web content. Since search 2.0 folders are specific to the content category, this would not be an issue for Search 2.0 and will be forced to 'all' here.
